Name: Raining Coins
About the game: It's raining gold coins! Come, play & catch them! (4K@120FPS) Help little Eve catch the gold coins! The skies have opened up but it’s not raining cats and dogs! It’s raining gold coins! Help poor Eve catch the gold coins and buy the toys she loves. 4K super addictive family game fun for kids, teenagers and grownups. Remastered 4K@120FPS. Designed for family and small kids. Super cute graphics & characters. 4 worlds & 80 exciting rounds to play. Dress Eve up with skirts, costumes and accessories! Get help if you need it.
